text: haey pimoun vea( kompir kuor an) mean kompir muoy robsa mousaea ( ta v rt) chea kardoeknoam ning chea kdei me tda krounea . haey nih(kompir kuor an) kuchea kompir del banhcheak( pi kompir moun ) chea pheasaea areab daembi dasatuen promean dl puok del bampean ning chea damnoeng rikreay samreab banda anak del sang ampeula
